<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Our Love Story ❤️</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
background:black;
color:white;
overflow-x:hidden;
}

/* 🎬 Background Video */
#bgVideo{
position:fixed;
top:0;
left:0;
width:100%;
height:100%;
object-fit:cover;
object-position:center 25%;
z-index:-2;
animation: zoomIn 20s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes zoomIn{
0%{transform:scale(1);}
100%{transform:scale(1.08);}
}

/* Dark Overlay */
.overlay{
position:fixed;
top:0;
left:0;
width:100%;
height:100%;
background:rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
z-index:-1;
}

/* Content */
.container{
padding:40px 20px;
text-align:center;
}

h1{
font-size:40px;
margin-bottom:30px;
color:#ff4d6d;
}

.gallery{
display:grid;
grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
gap:20px;
max-width:1200px;
margin:auto;
}

.gallery div{
background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
padding:15px;
border-radius:20px;
backdrop-filter:blur(10px);
transition:0.4s;
}

.gallery div:hover{
transform:scale(1.05);
}

.gallery img{
width:100%;
height:300px;
object-fit:cover;
border-radius:15px;
}

.gallery p{
margin-top:10px;
font-weight:500;
}

/* Punjabi Ending */
.ending{
margin-top:60px;
font-size:22px;
line-height:1.8;
color:#ffd6e0;
font-weight:600;
animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes fadeIn{
from{opacity:0;}
to{opacity:1;}
}

/* Mobile */
@media(max-width:768px){
h1{font-size:28px;}
.gallery img{height:220px;}
.ending{font-size:18px;}
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- Background Video -->
<video autoplay muted loop playsinline id="bgVideo">
<source src="video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
</video>

<div class="overlay"></div>

<div class="container">

<h1>Our Beautiful Memories ❤️</h1>

<div class="gallery">

<div>
<img src="photo1.jpg">
<p>First Smile I Fell For 😍</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo2.jpg">
<p>Miss Universe Of My Life 👑</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo3.jpg">
<p>Your Eyes = My Heaven ✨</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo4.jpg">
<p>Pure Beauty From God 🌸</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo5.jpg">
<p>That Cute Attitude 😎</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo6.jpg">
<p>My Forever Happiness 💕</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo7.jpg">
<p>Queen Of My Heart ❤️</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo8.jpg">
<p>My Peace & My Madness 💫</p>
</div>

<div>
<img src="photo9.jpg">
<p>Last But Always First In My Heart 💖</p>
</div>

</div>

<!-- Punjabi Lines After Last Photo -->
<div class="ending">
ਇਕ ਤੇਰੀ ਮੇਰੀ ਜੋੜੀ<br>
ਉੱਤੋਂ ਅਕਲ ਦੋਵਾਂ ਨੂੰ ਥੋੜੀ<br>
ਲੜਦੇ ਭਾਵੇ ਲੱਖ ਰਹੀਏ<br>
ਪਰ ਅੰਦਰੋ ਪਿਆਰ ਵੀ ਕਰਦੇ ਚੌਰੀ ਚੌਰੀ ❤️
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
